{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BbwsvUPKmP8nXy9UpjhNcq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. The ingress-nginx controller is running and uses the `ingress-nginx-controller` ConfigMap in the `ingress-nginx` namespace. The ConfigMap currently has no data.\n\nI need to:\n1. Enable OpenTelemetry in the ingress-nginx controller via ConfigMap\n2. Configure 100% sampling\n3. Set the log format to include trace and span IDs\n\nLet me check ingress-nginx documentation for the relevant ConfigMap keys:\n- `enable-opentelemetry: \"true\"` - enables OpenTelemetry\n- `opentelemetry-config` - path to OTel config file... or\n- `otlp-collector-host` - hostname of the OTel collector\n- `otlp-collector-port` - port of the OTel collector (default 4317)\n- `otel-sampler` - sampler type (AlwaysOn, AlwaysOff, ParentBased, TraceIdRatioBased)\n- `otel-sampler-ratio` - ratio for TraceIdRatioBased sampler\n- `log-format-upstream` - log format\n\nFor ingress-nginx v1.14.1, the OTel configuration is done through the ConfigMap. I'm looking at what keys are available for this version.\n\nThe ConfigMap needs `enable-opentelemetry: \"true\"` along with the collector host and port settings, sampler configuration for controlling trace sampling rates, and optional settings like operation name and span trust behavior. The log format can be customized to include the OpenTelemetry trace ID in the upstream logs. The log format needs to be a single line in the ConfigMap, even though it's displayed across multiple lines for readability in the task description. I'll construct it as one continuous string without actual newlines.\n\nWriting ConfigMap patch...\n\nOnce the controller picks up the changes, I'll make a test request and verify that the logs contain the OpenTelemetry trace and span IDs.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":709,"cache_read_input_tokens":30506,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":709},"output_tokens":44,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"61dea913-c3cc-4e8e-bc48-23fe0273004f","uuid":"aa8e1a98-bb09-4c38-91c1-8a3d90b08d9d","request_id":"req_011Cc4PfiSxq9RpNQTF5dKjX"}
